菜是宾客对餐厅菜肴品质直接认识，将会影响宾客可用餐的食欲和心情，（可先上土素菜）</section>	</section></fieldset><p>	&nbsp;</p><p style=\"\">	&nbsp;</p><fieldset :=\"\" eo.backgroundcolor=\"\" eo.bordercolor=\"\" eo.color=\"\" eo.fontfamily=\"\" eo.fontsize=\"\" eo.fontstyle=\"\" eo.fontweight=\"\" eo.textalign=\"\" eo.textdecoration=\"\" ng-click=\"oncg(\$event)\" ng-style=\" {&amp;#10;  \" stop-propagation=\"click mousedown mouseup\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; border-bottom: rgb(160,160,160) 1px solid; min-width: 0px; border-left: rgb(160,160,160) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 8px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: normal; text-indent: 0px; margin: 27px 16px 16px; padding-left: 16px; padding-right: 16px; font-family: inherit; max-width: 100%; word-wrap: break-word !important; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; color: rgb(160,160,160); font-size: 14px; border-top: rgb(160,160,160) 1px solid; font-weight: normal; border-right: rgb(160,160,160) 1px solid; word-spacing: 0px; padding-top: 8px; box-shadow: rgb(165, 165, 165) 5px 5px 2px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\" tn-page-editable=\"richtext1\" tn-page-editable-type=\"ed-type-rich-text\" ui-on-drop=\"block(\$event)\">	<section style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; BORDER-BOTTOM: medium none; BORDER-LEFT: medium none; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; MARGIN: -1.2em 0px 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; BORDER-TOP: medium none; BORDER-RIGHT: medium none; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">		<section style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">			<span :=\"\" eo.backgroundcolor=\"\" eo.bordercolor=\"\" eo.color=\"\" eo.fontfamily=\"\" eo.fontsize=\"\" eo.fontstyle=\"\" eo.fontweight=\"\" eo.textalign=\"\" eo.textdecoration=\"\" ng-click=\"oncg(\$event)\" ng-mode