: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">			4. 缺少服务礼貌用语，更没有亲切的沟通。</section>		<section style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">			5. 服务影响宾客用餐及宾客相互交谈。</section>		<section style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">			6. 服务不及时，经常出现空档。</section>		<section style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">			2）良好席间服务两要素：</section>		<section style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">			1. 服务耐心细致，主动热情，能善解人意。</section>		<section style=\"BOX-SIZING: border-box !important; PADDING-BOTTOM: 0px; FONT-STYLE: normal; MARGIN: 0px; PADDING-LEFT: 0px; PADDING-RIGHT: 0px; MAX-WIDTH: 100%; WORD-WRAP: break-word !important; PADDING-TOP: 0px\">			2. 规范的服务操作，及时、亲切的礼貌用语。</section>	</section></fieldset><p>	&nbsp;</p><p style=\"\">	&nbsp;</p><fieldset :=\"\" eo.backgroundcolor=\"\" eo.bordercolor=\"\" eo.color=\"\" eo.fontfamily=\"\" eo.fontsize=\"\" eo.fontstyle=\"\" eo.fontweight=\"\" eo.textalign=\"\" eo.textdecoration=\"\" ng-click=\"oncg(\$event)\" ng-style=\" {&amp;#10;  \" stop-propagation=\"click mousedown mouseup\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box !important; border-bottom: rgb(160,160,160) 1px solid; min-width: 0px; border-left: rgb(160,160,160) 1px solid; padding-bottom: 8px; text-transform: none; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); font-variant: normal; font-style: norma